00:34:18,790 --> 00:34:23,340
<i>Čože? Je to pravda?</i>

318
00:34:23,340 --> 00:34:26,150
<i>Viceprezident Ča Min-ho sa nezabil sám?</i>

319
00:34:26,150 --> 00:34:30,740
<i>To si myslia všetci. Okrem mňa.</i>

320
00:34:32,410 --> 00:34:40,200
