321
00:34:40,200 --> 00:34:44,550
<i>Ale ako tomu môžem veriť?</i>

322
00:34:45,420 --> 00:34:47,060
<i>Máš dôkaz?</i>

323
00:34:47,060 --> 00:34:50,790
<i>Na to som si ešte nespomenul.</i>

324
00:34:50,790 --> 00:34:51,680
<i>Čo?</i>

325
00:34:51,680 --> 00:34:55,230
